Run the following to download the Gradle wrapper JAR before first build:

  cd /data/data/com.termux/files/home/audiosub
  gradle wrapper --gradle-version 8.6

Or copy from an existing Gradle installation:
  cp ~/.gradle/wrapper/dists/gradle-8.6-bin/*/gradle-8.6/lib/gradle-wrapper.jar \
     gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
